---
<section id="protocol" class="bg-bg relative py-24">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary tracking-tight">标准化履约流程</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-text-light text-lg">每一步都有迹可循，让您的托付百分百安心。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col gap-8 relative pb-24">
    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="sticky top-24 w-full rounded-[3rem] bg-white border border-gray-200 shadow-xl p-8 md:p-16 min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden origin-top">
      <div class="absolute right-[-10%] top-[-10%] opacity-5">
        <svg class="w-96 h-96 animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl">
        <span class="font-mono text-accent font-bold text-xl mb-4 block">01</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary mb-6">精准调度与资质核查</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          依托20年积累的庞大运力池，快速匹配最优车型。严格核查司机"三证"，确保车辆健康、保险齐全，将风险拦截在装车之前。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="sticky top-32 w-full rounded-[3rem] bg-primary text-white shadow-xl p-8 md:p-16 min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden origin-top">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.2)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.2)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:20px_20px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accent shadow-[0_0_20px_var(--color-accent)] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl">
        <span class="font-mono text-accent font-bold text-xl mb-4 block">02</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6">管家式全程盯办</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          从装车点到卸货点，专属调度员建立微信群，实时播报在途位置。遇恶劣天气或堵车，第一时间预警并协助司机解决问题。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="sticky top-40 w-full rounded-[3rem] bg-accent text-white shadow-xl p-8 md:p-16 min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden origin-top">
      <div class="absolute right-[-5%] bottom-[-20%] opacity-20">
        <svg class="w-[600px] h-[300px]" viewBox="0 0 500 150" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-dasharray="1000" stroke-dashoffset="1000" class="protocol-dash" d="M0,75 L150,75 L175,25 L225,125 L250,75 L500,75" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl">
        <span class="font-mono text-white/70 font-bold text-xl mb-4 block">03</span>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6">安全交付与极速结算</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed">
          货物安全抵达后，协助跟进回单签收。财务中枢极速响应，对货主账单清晰透明，对司机运费结算痛快，绝不拖欠。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes dash {
    to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
  }
  .protocol-dash {
    animation: dash 3s linear infinite;
  }
</style>
